commit message: Android market publishing interface now requires a 512x512 icon as well. For now, I've just scaled the application icon up.
Move package= above installLocation= to avoid future merge conflicts. Add <support-screens> to fix display problems on high-density screen devices.

Allows app to resize to any screen size and use Honeycomb's Action Bar
for the menu.
